      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of superlative caliber. This specimen remains in impeccable showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior cabin that reflects meticulous stewardship. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been preserved to meet the most exacting standards of excellence. This represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the typical pre-owned market, offering an ownership experience indistinguishable from new.",
