    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total beauty. This car is in showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch, dent, or speck of dust to be found! It drives like it just rolled off the lot and has been pampered since day one. If you're looking for a ride that feels and looks brand new, this is the one. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
