      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true time-capsule vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior features a mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating and absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or door dings. Inside, the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the cabin still retains that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component functions perfectly, and the engine bay is detailed to show-quality standards. This car comes with a complete portfolio of service records, all original keys, and the factory window sticker. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor\u2014tight, responsive, and completely silent. Truly a rare find for a discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
