    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in flawless condition\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've kept it tucked away in the garage and babied it since day one. You won't find a single scratch or speck of dust on this beauty. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. Come check it out, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
