      "description": "This meticulously preserved specimen features a numbers-matching, high-revving power unit paired with a close-ratio manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. The valvetrain is whisper-quiet, showing no signs of eccentric wear, while the forced induction system holds peak boost pressure with zero shaft play in the turbines. The suspension geometry remains factory-precise, utilizing original-spec dampers and bushings for neutral handling and zero-lash steering feedback. Every fluid circuit has been flushed and pressurized to ensure thermal efficiency under load. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example with flawless panel gaps and a pristine undercarriage.",
